   Changes:
   - 0.3 (2003-12-09) - added support for character constants and C-style
                        hex and bin values (eg. 0xff, 0b11111111)
   - 0.2 (2003-12-04) - fixed CJNE, redefinition of constants is allowed
   - 0.1 (2003-11-02) - initial release

